cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper deals with embodied artificial intelligence and self-organization, which are closely related to robotics (cs.RO). The learning method proposed in the paper is based on maximizing predictive information, which is a common approach in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the analysis of the effect of robot chain length on overall behavior, which is related to control systems (cs.SY) and neural networks (cs.NE).
